# SPEC-2359 Phase W-12 Slice 5b (FR-353): the Work event log is the repo-local,
# git-tracked persistent core. Keep it tracked even if a broader `.gwt/` ignore
# rule is introduced. Derived (works.json) and volatile state stay in ~/.gwt.
!.gwt/work/
!.gwt/work/events.jsonl

